Sony Forecasts Full-Year Net of 80 Billion Yen, Below Estimates

-- B y   M a r i k o   Y a s u
-- 
2011-05-26T06:03:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/sony-forecasts-978-million-full-year-profit-below-analysts-estimates.html
Sony Corp. (6758)  forecast net income will
total 80 billion yen ($978 million) in the year to March 2012,
the Tokyo-based company said in a statement today. That compares
with the 115.9 billion yen average of 12 analyst estimates
compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mariko Yasu in 東京 at 
